These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, cricket
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, rose
There 2 different types of food: tomato, lettuce
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bike
1. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Sport      | cricket      | basketball    |
| Flower           | rose | daisy |
| Food   | tomato       | lettuce  |
| Transport     | airplane      | bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, siglo
House: futuristic, modern
2 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, police-officer
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
2. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the police-officer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Cigar          | siglo | cain |
| House   | futuristic       | modern         |
| Pet           | rabbit     | cat         |
| Job     | police-officer    | firefighter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
House: cottage, art-deco
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, pink
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, r&b
2 different games are played: go, bridge
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| House         | art-deco          | cottage |
| Color           | pink | aquamarine     |
| Music-Genre   | folk            | r&b         |
| Game     | bridge         | go   |

 #################################

 
