3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |
| Pet    | hedgehog     | turtle           |
| Color        | orange      | chestnut    |
| Hobby       | dancing    | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | horror          |

