.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, fisherman
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, jazz
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, rose
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the manager##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of folk is the person who growsrose##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Job      | fisherman     | manager |
| Movie-Genre          | sports   | fantasy |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | folk     |
| Flower     | orchid | rose     |

 